data.description: Nearly new 4 bedroom/2.5 bath home with 2 car garage on a full unfinished basement and tucked away in a small quiet community (no  HOA) in Temple. This home is extremely clean and well-maintained, and you'll feel right at home as soon as you walk in. The floorplan is perfect for entertaining and everyday living. On the main floor, you'll notice the beautiful large dining room with beamed ceilings,  spacious kitchen with quartz countertops, large island with room for seating, dual walk-in pantries, large living room with a cozy fireplace, and tons of natural light. Also on the main floor is a convenient half bath, as well as a door going out to the balcony overlooking the private backyard with views of the woods and pond! Upstairs are all 4 of the bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, as well as the laundry room. You'll be amazed at the size of the primary suite, along with dual walk-in closets, and the well-appointed spa-like bathroom. The remaining 3 bedrooms are good-sized, each with tray ceilings and walk-in closets. Downstairs in the basement, you'll notice poured concrete wall construction, plumbing for another bathroom, and enough height to finish out comfortably, making the possibilities endless. This home is sure to check off all the boxes! Be sure to check out the Zillow 3D tour!
